James Chen
Director of Guest Relations
Coastal Resort Group
www.coastalresortgroup.com

Unsubscribe from event invitations: coastalresortgroup.com/unsubscribe', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["Register by March 15 for 20% off','visit coastalresortgroup.com/conference','Spaces are limited to 250 guests','Complimentary room block at 30% discount"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Early bird deadline creates promotional urgency typical of event marketing — not account-threat urgency','Registration link directs to the legitimate company domain with a clear event-specific path','Limited seating is disclosed transparently as a fact about venue capacity',' not a scarcity scare tactic','Concrete event details (date',' location',' program agenda',' pricing) confirm this is a real event',' not a bait-and-switch"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate event invitation from Coastal Resort Group. James Chen is promoting a genuine conference with transparent pricing, a specific venue, detailed agenda, and verifiable registration details. The legitimacy indicators include: sender domain matches the company, all event logistics are explicit and checkable (date, location, call-in number), registration is via the company''s legitimate domain, there is no credential request, and the footer includes an unsubscribe link. The early bird discount is a standard promotional device, not a false account warning. A recipient can verify this event independently by calling the phone number or visiting the website.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

