VALUES ('real-p-1772686641954', 'email', TRUE, 'hard', 'David Okafor <d.okafor@serenehotels-corp.com>', 'Vendor Invoice and Commission Structure Update', 'David,

I hope you''re having a productive quarter. We''re writing to inform you of a change to our commission settlement process for all contracted properties, effective immediately. After a comprehensive audit of our vendor payment infrastructure, we''ve streamlined the approval workflow to reduce payment cycle times and improve transparency.

