VALUES ('real-l-1772686660860', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'IT Support <itsupport@urbanlivingpm.com>', 'MobileKey Access Renewal — Action Required by January 20', 'Hi Priya,

Your MobileKey access certificate will expire on January 20, 2025. This certificate allows you to remotely unlock tenant doors and access common areas via your phone. To renew it, you''ll need to complete a short recertification process through our property access portal.

Here''s what to do:

1. Log in to the access portal at [urbanlivingpm.com/mobilekey-admin](https://access.urbanlivingpm.com/mobilekey-admin) using your staff credentials
2. Click "Renew Certificate" in the left menu
3. Confirm your current phone number and device type
4. Accept the updated access policy (updated Jan 5 to include after-hours lockout protocols)
5. Submit — you''ll receive a confirmation email within 2 hours

If you don''t renew before January 20, your MobileKey access will be disabled. If you have trouble with any step or don''t have MobileKey configured, reply to this email or call IT support at (555) 402-6655 ext. 110.

IT Support Team
Urban Living Property Management
itsupport@urbanlivingpm.com', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["Your MobileKey access certificate will expire on January 20',' 2025','Log in to the access portal at [urbanlivingpm.com/mobilekey-admin]','reply to this email or call IT support at (555) 402-6655 ext. 110"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Certificate expiration is a routine technical maintenance task',' not a credential reset or account takeover','The linked portal is the company''s legitimate access management system; the URL domain matches the sender''s domain','IT support provides multiple ways to verify (email reply',' phone with extension) and includes timeout information"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate IT system maintenance notification. The sender is the company''s IT support team using the company domain, the technical action (certificate renewal) is routine and system-critical in property management, and the deadline is realistic (13 days away). The email includes clear step-by-step instructions and multiple support contact methods. Although it asks for login credentials, the linked portal is the company''s own system, and the sender provides ways to verify the request through alternative channels.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

