VALUES ('real-l-1772686909038', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'James Liu <communications@capitalinvestmentgroup.com>', 'Introducing CapitalIQ Pro: Advanced Market Analytics for Institutional Investors', 'Dear Aisha,

Capital Investment Group is proud to announce the launch of CapitalIQ Pro, a new advanced market analytics platform designed specifically for institutional investors, portfolio managers, and wealth management firms.

Built over three years with input from more than 500 institutional clients, CapitalIQ Pro delivers institutional-grade tools that were previously available only to mega-cap hedge funds and investment banks. We''re now making this technology accessible to mid-market and regional investment firms.

Key Features:

Real-Time Market Intelligence — Access live data feeds from 30+ global exchanges, commodity markets, and alternative asset classes. Customizable watchlists, alerts, and scenario modeling help you identify opportunities before competitors.

Advanced Risk Analytics — Perform stress testing, value-at-risk (VaR) calculations, and correlation analysis across your entire portfolio. Drill down to individual holdings or zoom out to sector-level exposure in seconds.

Collaborative Portfolio Reviews — Built-in annotation tools let teams comment on trades, flag concerns, and collaborate in real-time. Full audit trails capture all decisions for compliance and reporting.

Seamless Integration — CapitalIQ Pro integrates with Bloomberg, FactSet, and major custodian APIs, so you keep your existing workflows. No rip-and-replace required.

Pricing:

CapitalIQ Pro is available on a tiered subscription model starting at $2,500 per month for single-user access and scaling to enterprise licenses for larger teams. The first 100 institutional clients to sign up before June 30 will receive 25% off the first year.

To schedule a personalized demo, visit demo.capitalinvestmentgroup.com/capitalize-pro or contact our enterprise sales team at sales@capitalinvestmentgroup.com. We typically schedule demos within 24–48 hours of inquiry.

We''re confident that CapitalIQ Pro will become an essential tool in your investment workflow. Let''s talk about how it can help your firm make faster, smarter decisions.

Best regards,
James Liu
Head of Product Marketing
Capital Investment Group Inc.
1200 Wall Street, New York, NY 10005
sales@capitalinvestmentgroup.com | 1-800-555-0145
www.capitalinvestmentgroup.com

To unsubscribe from product announcements, visit capitalinvestmentgroup.com/preferences.', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["The first 100 institutional clients to sign up before June 30 will receive 25% off the first year','To schedule a personalized demo',' visit demo.capitalinvestmentgroup.com/capitalize-pro','To unsubscribe from product announcements',' visit capitalinvestmentgroup.com/preferences"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Product announcement includes technical specifications (30+ exchanges',' VaR calculations',' Bloomberg/FactSet integration',' audit trails) that demonstrate a real product offering — phishing announcements lack such verifiable details','Demo link uses a legitimate company subdomain demo.capitalinvestmentgroup.com — no lookalike domain or suspicious redirect','Early-adopter discount is time-limited but not urgent in tone — promotional urgency about a deal is legitimate; phishing urgency is about account security or verification"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate product announcement from an investment services firm. The sender is identified by role and name, and all domain references match the sender domain and signature. The announcement provides substantive product details (real-time market data, risk analytics, collaboration tools, API integrations) and transparent pricing information. The early-adopter discount is a standard marketing incentive with a clear deadline. Users are directed to a demo scheduling page on the legitimate company domain, not to a credential submission form. The unsubscribe option is provided. This is professional B2B marketing communication.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

