VALUES ('real-l-1772679798600', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'Guardian Health Plus <billing@guardianhealthplus.com>', 'Your Quarterly Premium Renewal – Policy GP-556421', 'Hello Sarah,

This is a courtesy reminder that your health insurance policy is scheduled to renew on February 28, 2025. Your quarterly premium payment is due by that date to maintain continuous coverage.

Policy Details:
Policy Number: GP-556421
Coverage Type: Family Health Plus
Current Quarterly Premium: $1,847.50
Billing Cycle: January 1 – March 31, 2025
Payment Due Date: February 28, 2025

Your payment has been automatically processed on your stored payment method (Visa ending in 4521) as of today, January 22, 2025. No further action is required. You will receive a payment confirmation and receipt within 24 hours.

Your coverage remains active during the billing cycle. To view your full policy summary, claims history, or to update your payment method, please log into the Guardian Health Plus member portal at members.guardianhealthplus.com.

Thank you for your continued business with Guardian Health Plus. If you have questions about your renewal or billing, contact our member services team at 1-855-GHP-CARE (1-855-447-2273).

Regards,
Billing Services Team
Guardian Health Plus', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["Your payment has been automatically processed on your stored payment method (Visa ending in 4521)','Your coverage remains active during the billing cycle','No further action is required"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["The partial card number (last 4 digits) confirms the payment was processed against the claimant''s own registered payment method',' not a request for new credentials or payment details.','The explicit statement that coverage remains active shows this is a routine renewal confirmation',' not a payment demand or coverage cancellation notice.','The ''no further action required'' language combined with automatic processing is typical of legitimate recurring billing notifications and indicates this is transactional',' not a call to action."]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate quarterly premium renewal confirmation from a health insurance provider. It includes the policy number, coverage dates, specific premium amount, the date payment was processed, the last 4 digits of the card used (confirming the insured''s own stored method), and a clear statement that no action is required. The sender email matches the company domain (guardianhealthplus.com), and the tone is informational rather than urgent. A player might suspect this because it mentions billing and requires payment, but the key indicators of legitimacy are the automatic processing notification, the partial card number that matches the customer''s own payment method, the explicit ''no action required'' statement, and the detailed policy information tied to the customer''s account. This is routine transactional communication.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

