VALUES ('real-p-1772682131320', 'email', TRUE, 'medium', 'Robert Chen <recruitment@advancecareer-solutions.com>', 'Your Referral Bonus Is Pending – Claim It Now', 'Hi Keiko,

Great news! You''ve been approved for a referral bonus of $2,500 for bringing in a qualified candidate. However, to process and distribute this bonus to your account, we need to verify your identity in our employee rewards portal.

