Don''t miss out on your well-deserved bonus! The link will expire in 48 hours.

Congratulations,
Robert Chen
Recruiter & Talent Acquisition Lead
Advance Career Solutions
support@advancecareer.com', 'credential-harvest', 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["log in with your employee credentials to claim your bonus','https://rewards.advancecareer-net.com/claim-bonus','The link will expire in 48 hours"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["The credential request is justified by a financial incentive (referral bonus)',' which motivates the recipient to act quickly without verification.','The link domain (advancecareer-net.com) differs from the legitimate company domain in the signature (advancecareer.com)',' indicating an attacker-controlled phishing site.','The 48-hour expiration deadline creates artificial urgency',' pressuring the recipient to log in immediately rather than verifying the sender''s legitimacy."]']::TEXT[], 'This is a medium-difficulty credential-harvest phishing email that uses financial incentive as motivation. The attacker impersonates a recruiter and frames the credential request as a necessary step to claim a referral bonus. The email leverages greed and urgency (limited-time offer, expiring link) to override the recipient''s skepticism. The tell is the domain mismatch: the FROM address and link use advancecareer-net.com, but the signature references advancecareer.com. An employee excited about a monetary reward may not scrutinize the domain closely.', 'generated', 'v1')
