VALUES ('real-l-1772686731646', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'Nadia Okafor <updates@verticalstudios.com>', 'Behind the Scenes: How We Made Our Viral Documentary – New Mini-Series Available Now', 'Hello Marcus,

Vertical Studios is proud to announce the premiere of a new four-part mini-series: "Making It: The Production Diary of ''Beneath the Surface''." If you''ve watched our award-winning documentary "Beneath the Surface" on any of the major streaming platforms, you''ll love this exclusive behind-the-scenes look at how we brought the story to life.

Over four 20-minute episodes, you''ll follow our production team through:
- Location scouting in three continents
- Interviews with our director, cinematographer, and lead researchers
- The challenges of filming in extreme environments
- Post-production secrets: how we achieved the stunning colour grade and sound design
- The emotional journey of telling a story that mattered to us

Each episode is paired with downloadable production notes, featuring our director''s personal reflections and technical specifications on cameras, lenses, and audio equipment used.

Where to watch: The mini-series is available exclusively on the Vertical Studios members platform. If you''re already a member, log in to your account and navigate to "Originals" to start watching. New members can join for $9.99/month or $79.99/year with a 7-day free trial.

Schedule: New episodes release every Thursday starting March 21st. All four episodes will be available by April 11th.

We think this will resonate with anyone interested in documentary production, filmmaking techniques, or the stories behind the stories. We''d love to hear what you think—share your thoughts with us on social media or reply with feedback.

Thank you for your continued support of independent documentary work.

Warm regards,
Nadia Okafor
Content Director
Vertical Studios
www.verticalstudios.com
updates@verticalstudios.com
(416) 555-0192

Manage your subscriptions and preferences: www.verticalstudios.com/account', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["New four-part mini-series: ''Making It: The Production Diary of ''Beneath the Surface''','New members can join for $9.99/month or $79.99/year with a 7-day free trial','New episodes release every Thursday starting March 21st"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["This is a content announcement with clear premiere dates and subscription pricing—legitimate marketing content',' not a phishing lure.','The email directs existing members to log into their account normally and offers a free trial for new members—no credential verification request.','The release schedule is transparent and specific',' showing the company is committed to the content series."]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate content announcement email from a media production studio. The sender (Nadia Okafor) is clearly identified, the FROM domain (verticalstudios.com) matches the company being promoted, and the email describes a real new series with concrete details: episode count, duration, topics covered, release schedule, and pricing. The call to action is straightforward—log into your existing account or sign up for a membership—with transparent pricing and a free trial option. There is no request for credentials or account verification. A player should note the specific content details, the clear company identity, the transparent pricing structure, and the absence of credential requests as signals of legitimacy.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

