VALUES ('real-l-1772678014850', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'Matter Updates <updates@brookfieldlegal.com>', 'Discovery Deadline Reminder – Matter #BL-2024-001523', 'Hi Chen,

This is an automated reminder regarding an upcoming deadline for your matter with us.

Matter Number: BL-2024-001523
Client: Westbrook Industries, Inc.
Current Phase: Discovery
Deadline: March 1, 2024
Deadline Type: Interrogatory Responses Due

Please note that interrogatories from opposing counsel are due to be answered and returned by 5:00 PM EST on March 1, 2024. Our discovery team is reviewing the responses and will have a draft ready for your review by February 27, 2024.

Next Steps:
1. Review our draft responses by February 27
2. Provide any corrections or additions by February 28
3. We will finalize and file by the deadline

No immediate action is required from you at this time. We will send a follow-up reminder with the draft responses by February 25, 2024. Please mark your calendar to ensure timely review.

If you have questions about this deadline or need to discuss strategy, contact your assigned counsel, David Okafor, at d.okafor@brookfieldlegal.com or call (555) 456-7823.

Best regards,
Matter Update System
Brookfield Legal Group
567 Litigation Plaza, Floor 8
Houston, TX 77002', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["Matter #BL-2024-001523','Deadline: March 1',' 2024','Interrogatory Responses Due','No immediate action is required from you at this time"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Specific matter number and client name confirm this reminder is tied to a real matter in the firm''s case management system','The deadline type (interrogatory responses) and specific date are details the client would recognize from their discovery schedule','The phased next-steps (review draft',' provide corrections',' finalize) show realistic litigation workflow and confirm this is an operational reminder',' not a phishing attempt','The statement that no immediate action is required',' combined with a clear timeline for the firm''s work',' shows this is a courtesy update and not a pressure tactic"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate transactional matter reminder from a law firm''s case management system. It notifies the client of an upcoming deadline (interrogatory responses) that they would be aware of, and outlines the firm''s plan to prepare draft responses for client review. The email includes the specific matter number, client name, deadline date, and a clear timeline for next steps. The sender domain matches the firm''s legitimate address, there is no credential request, and the tone is informative and professional. A player might worry because it mentions a deadline, but the absence of urgency language (''No immediate action is required''), the detailed project plan, and the invitation to discuss strategy with assigned counsel all confirm this is legitimate case management communication.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

