VALUES ('real-p-1772682130779', 'email', TRUE, 'easy', 'Digital Rights Management <drm@audiovoxmedia.net>', 'CRITICAL: Your Music Licensing Rights Will Expire in 12 Hours', 'Hello Chen,

AudioVox Media has detected that your music licensing rights are set to expire in 12 hours. Once expired, your tracks will be removed from all streaming platforms and your royalty account will be locked.

