Do not delay.

Digital Rights Management Team
AudioVox Media
[www.audiovoxmedia.com](www.audiovoxmedia.com)', 'urgency', 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["Your music licensing rights are set to expire in 12 hours','your tracks will be removed from all streaming platforms and your royalty account will be locked','http://audiovoxmedia-rights-renew.info/licensing"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Legitimate licensing platforms provide 30–90 days'' notice before contract expiration; a 12-hour notice for critical rights renewal is unrealistic and designed to bypass verification.','Threatening immediate removal of content and account lockout without prior warning is a phishing scare tactic; real platforms would notify users much earlier.','The renewal link uses .info TLD (audiovoxmedia-rights-renew.info) and does not match the legitimate audiovoxmedia.com domain in the signature. This domain mismatch is the forensic anchor."]']::TEXT[], 'This is a phishing email using urgency around music licensing and revenue loss to pressure Chen into clicking a malicious link. The attacker impersonates AudioVox Media''s Digital Rights Management team and threatens immediate removal of all music tracks and royalty account lockout within 12 hours. The renewal link uses a lookalike domain (audiovoxmedia-rights-renew.info) designed to harvest credentials. The unrealistic 12-hour deadline for such a critical action, combined with the threat of content removal and revenue loss, are classic phishing urgency tactics targeting creative professionals.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

