VALUES ('real-p-1772679991342', 'email', TRUE, 'easy', 'Michael Okafor <m.okafor@capitalrealestateinvest.com>', 'Investment Property Portfolio Review', 'Hi Marcus,

Thank you for your continued partnership with Capital Real Estate Investments. As your portfolio manager, I want to ensure you have visibility into your current holdings and their performance metrics.

I''ve prepared a comprehensive portfolio review that includes property valuations, rental income analysis, and market forecasting for the next fiscal year. To access your personalized investment dashboard and download the full report, please log in through the secure portal link provided below.

Access your investment dashboard: capital-realestate-portal.net/dashboard/login

The dashboard will display your current net worth across all properties, monthly cash flow projections, and recommendations for portfolio optimization. I recommend reviewing this material before our quarterly call next week so we can discuss any questions or strategic adjustments.

Please let me know once you''ve accessed the portal and reviewed the materials.

Best regards,
Michael Okafor
Senior Portfolio Manager
Capital Real Estate Investments
www.capitalrealestategroup.com', 'fluent-prose', 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["capital-realestate-portal.net/dashboard/login','log in through the secure portal','access your personalized investment dashboard"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["The link domain ''capital-realestate-portal.net'' does not match the company website ''capitalrealestategroup.com'' shown in the signature. The attacker used a hyphenated lookalike to appear legitimate while directing to a phishing site.','Requesting login credentials to view investment portfolio information through an email link is not standard practice — legitimate investment firms use pre-authenticated accounts or in-person verification for sensitive financial data.','The professional tone and specific portfolio details (cash flow projections',' quarterly calls) create confidence in the sender despite the suspicious link',' making this an effective social engineering attack."]']::TEXT[], 'This is a phishing email using polished, professional language and investment industry terminology to mask a credential harvesting attack against a real estate investor. The email reads naturally and includes contextually appropriate details (portfolio performance, quarterly meetings, optimization strategies). The phishing mechanism is a fake investment dashboard link designed to capture login credentials. The key tell is the domain mismatch: the FROM address uses ''capitalrealestateinvest.com'' but the signature references ''capitalrealestategroup.com'', while the malicious link uses ''capital-realestate-portal.net''. The request to log in to view sensitive portfolio information through an email link, combined with high-value financial context, makes this phishing attack effective despite its fluent, professional presentation.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

