VALUES ('real-p-1772686729082', 'email', TRUE, 'easy', 'Support Team <support@realtyhub-secure.net>', 'Urgent: Verify Your RealtyHub Account Access', 'Dear Customer,

We have detected unusual activity on your RealtyHub property management account. For your security, we need you to verify your credentials immediately.

Please click the link below to confirm your identity and regain access to your listings:

www.realtyhub-secure.net/verify-account

This verification is required within 24 hours to prevent account suspension.

Thank you,
RealtyHub Support Team', 'authority-impersonation', 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["verify your credentials immediately','www.realtyhub-secure.net/verify-account','account suspension"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Legitimate property management platforms never ask for credential verification via email — this is a classic phishing tactic','The sender domain is realtyhub-secure.net',' not the real RealtyHub domain (realtyhub.com) — ''secure'' is a common phishing indicator','Artificial urgency and threat of account suspension are used to pressure the recipient into acting without verification"]']::TEXT[], 'This is phishing. The attacker impersonates RealtyHub support by using a lookalike domain (realtyhub-secure.net instead of realtyhub.com). The email uses authority impersonation and urgency tactics to trick the recipient into clicking a malicious link and entering credentials. Real property management platforms never request credential verification via email links. The sender domain is the forensic tell — the ''secure'' subdomain is not part of the legitimate brand.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

