VALUES ('real-p-1772686646914', 'email', TRUE, 'easy', 'Priya Kapoor <noreply@sunbelt-power.org>', 'Your Electricity Bill is Ready - Download Now', 'Hi Aisha,

Your August electricity bill is now ready. To view and download your bill, please click the link below and log in with your username and password.

