Manage event invitations: [Preferences](https://www.pinnacle-goods.com/account/event-preferences)', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["You are cordially invited to an exclusive VIP shopping night and fashion showcase','VIP-only discount: 20% off all purchases during the event','RSVP by March 18','Manage event invitations: [Preferences]"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Event invitation includes specific date',' time',' address',' and RSVP deadline — legitimate logistics','VIP discount applies only at the event',' not through a suspicious link requesting credentials','RSVP mechanism uses a legitimate event registration page within company domain','Preference management link provided — compliant marketing communication"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate VIP event invitation from Pinnacle Goods. The email includes verifiable event details (date, time, location, dress code, agenda), explains member benefits (early product access, discount, raffle), and provides clear RSVP instructions with a specific deadline. The sender (Katrina Volkova, VIP Customer Relations Manager) is identified with company contact information. No credentials, passwords, or account verification is requested. The RSVP mechanism uses a legitimate event registration page, and preference management is clearly offered.', 'generated', 'v1')
