VALUES ('real-l-1772682233359', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'Public Records Request Division <records-team@clerk.municipal.gov>', 'Your Public Records Request Has Been Fulfilled', 'Dear Chen,

Your public records request submitted on March 10, 2025, has been fulfilled and your documents are now ready for collection or download.

