If you have questions about the records, the redactions, or would like to request additional documents, please reply to this email or contact our office at (555) 678-9012. Our office is open Monday–Friday, 9 a.m.–5 p.m. local time.

Thank you for your interest in public records.

Best regards,
Public Records Clerk
