City of Westfield
www.clerk.municipal.gov', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["Request ID: FOIA-2025-003847','completed within the statutory 10-day response window','Some pages have been redacted in accordance with state exemptions"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["FOIA request ID ties this to a specific',' tracked request the recipient initiated — this proves the email is responding to a known action',' not phishing.','Reference to legal response deadlines demonstrates this is complying with actual law',' a detail phishers would rarely include accurately.','Professional mention of redaction protocol and legal exemptions shows institutional knowledge; phishing emails would skip such procedural details."]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate public records fulfillment notice from a municipal clerk''s office. The email includes a FOIA request ID, legal compliance details, and multiple attached documents — all correct for government records responses. A player might worry because it involves legal documents, but the professional adherence to public records law, the transparent explanation of redactions, and the complete absence of urgency or credential requests confirm legitimacy.', 'generated', 'v1')
