VALUES ('real-l-1772686808218', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'Treasury Solutions <treasury@mercantilebanking.com>', 'New Payment Processing Option: Same-Day ACH for Business Clients', 'Thomas,

Mercantile Banking is launching Same-Day ACH (Automated Clearing House) processing for our business and commercial clients. This new service allows you to send and receive ACH payments that settle the same business day, rather than waiting 1–2 days with standard ACH.

Benefits:
- Improved cash flow: funds arrive same day instead of next business day
- Enhanced supplier relationships: pay vendors faster when you need to
- Better liquidity management: collect receivables more quickly
- Reduced working capital: fewer float days mean less cash tied up
- Seamless integration: works with your existing Mercantile banking portal

How It Works:
Same-Day ACH follows the same easy steps as regular ACH but settles by 5 PM ET the same business day. Transactions must be initiated by 10:30 AM ET to qualify for same-day processing.

Pricing:
- Setup: Free
- Per-transaction fee: $0.50 per Same-Day ACH payment (vs. $0.25 for standard ACH)
- Monthly cap: None

Eligible customers can enable Same-Day ACH immediately through their Treasury Portal or by contacting their dedicated Mercantile relationship manager. First 100 customers to activate receive a $100 credit toward same-day ACH fees.

To activate: [Mercantile Treasury Portal](https://mercantilebanking.com/treasury) or call your relationship manager

Learn more: [Same-Day ACH FAQ](https://mercantilebanking.com/same-day-ach-faq) | [Technical Integration Guide](https://mercantilebanking.com/sameday-ach-guide)

Best regards,
Mercantile Banking Treasury Solutions Team
Mercantile Banking Corp
600 Market Street, Suite 1000
San Francisco, CA 94102
Phone: 1-888-MERCANTILE (1-888-637-2268)

Manage Treasury Services communications: [Settings](https://mercantilebanking.com/treasury-prefs)', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["funds arrive same day instead of next business day','First 100 customers to activate receive a $100 credit','Setup: Free"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Service pricing is clearly disclosed and incremental (additional $0.25 per transaction) — transparent business practice',' not a hidden cost scheme','First-mover incentive ($100 credit) is real but not deceptive urgency — standard new-product promotion','Sender domain matches bank',' relationship manager support offered',' settings/preference management provided"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate business banking service announcement from Mercantile Banking''s Treasury Solutions team. The email introduces a real payment processing feature (Same-Day ACH) with clear operational details: cutoff time (10:30 AM ET), settlement window (by 5 PM same day), and transparent pricing ($0.50/transaction vs. $0.25 for standard ACH). The service is free to activate with a limited-time early-adopter credit ($100 for first 100 customers), which is a realistic promotional incentive, not artificial urgency. The call to action is to activate through the existing portal or contact a relationship manager—normal banking procedures. The sender address matches the bank''s domain and support resources are provided. This is genuine commercial banking marketing.', 'generated', 'v1')
