VALUES ('real-l-1772822919680', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'CrossTown Logistics <no-reply@crosstownlogistics.io>', 'Your bill of lading has been generated — Shipment CTL-445678 ready to ship', 'Hello Chen,

Your bill of lading has been generated and your shipment is ready for dispatch. All documentation has been completed and filed.

