Regards,
Public Safety Records Division', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["Reference #BG-2024-549187','Results Status: CLEAR','Reports are valid for 30 days"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Unique reference number allows verification of this specific background check request through official channels','Clear status statement (''CLEAR'') is a definitive transactional outcome',' not a request for action','30-day validity window is a standard document control measure for background check reports used for employment"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate government transactional email confirming completion of a background check. It includes a unique reference number, check type, dates, results status, and access instructions for a secure portal. The sender is a public records division, the email includes a security note about a PIN sent via SMS, and there is no request for personal information or payment. A player might flag the ''do not ignore discrepancies'' language, but this is a standard fraud-alert reminder and does not constitute urgency or a phishing technique.', 'generated', 'v1')
