VALUES ('real-l-1772678902764', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'Deepak Kumar <marketing@acmereditfinance.com>', 'Acme Credit Finance Now Offers Credit-Building Accounts — Build Your Score Today', 'Hi Tom,

Acme Credit Finance is launching a new Credit-Building Account designed specifically for people working to improve their credit scores. Whether you''re recovering from past financial challenges, establishing credit for the first time, or rebuilding after a major life event, this product can help.

How It Works:

A Credit-Building Account is a secured savings account paired with a small credit line that reports your payment activity to all three credit bureaus. You deposit money (starting at just $200), and we lend you against that deposit. As you make on-time payments, your credit score improves — and after 12 months, you can graduate to an unsecured card or access better interest rates on loans.

Key Benefits:

No Credit Check Required — Unlike traditional credit cards, there''s no hard inquiry or credit approval process. Everyone qualifies, regardless of current score or history.

Low Cost — No annual fees, no prepayment penalties, and no hidden charges. Interest rates are transparent and competitive.

Guaranteed Improvement — Most participants see a 50–100 point credit score increase within 12 months of consistent on-time payments. Results vary based on individual circumstances and credit history.

Flexible Terms — Deposit amounts range from $200 to $2,500, and you choose your own repayment timeline (3, 6, 12, or 24 months).

Full Account Access — Your deposited funds are held in a secure savings account earning interest (currently 4.5% APY). You can withdraw the deposit if you choose to close the account, though early closure may impact your credit-building progress.

Who Should Consider This:

You''re rebuilding after bankruptcy or delinquency. You''re establishing credit as a new adult or immigrant. You''re returning to creditworthiness after a difficult financial period. You want to improve your credit before applying for a mortgage or auto loan.

Next Steps:

Learn more at creditbuilding.acmereditfinance.com, where you can see personalized projections based on your current score and desired improvement timeline. The application takes about 10 minutes and is completely online — no in-person visit required.

Our credit coaching team is also available to answer questions about building and maintaining good credit. Reach out at coaching@acmereditfinance.com or call 1-888-555-0191 (Monday–Friday, 9 AM–7 PM ET; Saturday 10 AM–4 PM ET).

Your path to better credit starts here.

Best regards,
Deepak Kumar
Consumer Products Marketing
Acme Credit Finance Inc.
1400 Tech Boulevard, Austin, TX 78701
www.acmereditfinance.com | marketing@acmereditfinance.com

You''re receiving this email because you''ve shown interest in credit products or have an Acme Credit Finance account. To unsubscribe from marketing emails, visit acmereditfinance.com/preferences.', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["Most participants see a 50–100 point credit score increase within 12 months of consistent on-time payments','Learn more at creditbuilding.acmereditfinance.com','You''re receiving this email because you''ve shown interest in credit products or have an Acme Credit Finance account. To unsubscribe from marketing emails',' visit acmereditfinance.com/preferences"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Product explanation includes realistic terms and disclaimers (''results vary based on individual circumstances',''' ''early closure may impact credit-building progress'') rather than guaranteed outcomes — legitimate financial product marketing includes caveats','Application link creditbuilding.acmereditfinance.com uses the legitimate company domain — not a lookalike or suspicious redirect','No credential request or account verification demand; users are simply directed to learn more and apply online through the legitimate company site"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate product marketing email from a credit finance company. The sender is identified by role, and all domain references match the sender domain. The announcement describes a real financial product (secured credit-building accounts) with specific features (no credit check, transparent fees, credit bureau reporting, flexible deposit amounts), realistic results ranges, and clear eligibility criteria. The marketing includes appropriate disclaimers about variability in outcomes. There is no false urgency, no credential request, and no deceptive claims. The application link uses the legitimate company domain. The unsubscribe option is provided. This is standard consumer financial marketing communication.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

