VALUES ('real-l-1772822918003', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'Harlow Equipment Co. <marketing@harlowequipment.com>', 'Introducing the ProDrive 900 Series — Precision Torque for Heavy-Duty Lines', 'Hi Marcus,

After two years of field testing alongside our partners in automotive stamping and structural steel fabrication, we''re proud to finally introduce the ProDrive 900 Series pneumatic torque tools to the broader market.

The 900 Series was designed from the ground up to address the feedback we kept hearing from floor supervisors: inconsistent torque output under high-cycle loads, and tools that couldn''t survive a 12-hour shift without recalibration. We''ve addressed both. The 900 Series maintains ±1.5% torque accuracy across 10,000 consecutive cycles, and its hardened composite housing is rated for continuous industrial use in environments up to 60°C.

For assembly lines running mixed fastener sizes, the quick-swap anvil system lets operators change between ¼", 3/8", and ½" drive configurations in under 20 seconds — no tools required. Each unit ships factory-calibrated with a full ISO 6789 certificate included.

We''re offering introductory pricing through the end of this quarter. The 900-15 (150 Nm) starts at $489 per unit with volume discounts available at 10, 25, and 50+ units. Our team is also offering free on-site demos at qualifying facilities in the Northeast and Midwest through November.

To see the full spec sheet, watch the 900 Series in action on the assembly line, or request a demo visit, head over to our product page at [harlowequipment.com/prodrive900](https://www.harlowequipment.com/prodrive900).

We think this is the torque tool your line has been waiting for, and we''d love to show you why.

Best regards,
Derek Halverson
Product Marketing Manager, Harlow Equipment Co.
harlowequipment.com | 1-800-442-0391
216 Industrial Parkway, Cleveland, OH 44114

You''re receiving this email because you subscribed to Harlow Equipment product updates. [Unsubscribe](https://www.harlowequipment.com/unsubscribe) | [View in browser](https://www.harlowequipment.com/email/prodrive900)', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["introductory pricing through the end of this quarter','harlowequipment.com | 1-800-442-0391\n216 Industrial Parkway',' Cleveland',' OH 44114','You''re receiving this email because you subscribed to Harlow Equipment product updates."]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Pricing urgency tied to a quarter-end deal — standard promotional language about a discount window',' not an account threat. No credential request or account action involved.','Physical street address',' phone number',' and domain all match the FROM sender — consistent company identity across the entire email.','Explicit subscription context explains why the recipient received this. A legitimate sender explains the mailing relationship; phishing emails rarely do."]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate product launch marketing email from Harlow Equipment Co. The FROM domain matches the website and signature domain exactly. The urgency is promotional (a pricing window), not account-based. No credentials are requested, an unsubscribe link is present, and a physical business address is included. These are all hallmarks of compliant commercial email.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

