VALUES ('real-l-1772686828894', 'email', FALSE, 'medium', 'Communications <comms@westminstercredit.com>', 'Introducing Westminster Credit Union''s Scholarship Program – Apply Now for 2025', 'Hello Keiko,

Westminster Credit Union is pleased to announce the launch of our annual scholarship program for the 2025–2026 academic year. We''re committed to supporting education in the communities we serve, and we''re offering $250,000 in total scholarships to eligible students.

Program Details:
- Scholarship Amount: $2,500 to $10,000 per recipient
- Number of Awards: Up to 30 scholarships
- Eligibility: High school seniors or current undergraduate/graduate students; member or family member of Westminster Credit Union member
- GPA Requirement: Minimum 3.0 GPA
- Application Deadline: January 15, 2025

Application Process:
1. Complete the online application at [Westminster Scholarship Portal](https://westminstercredit.com/scholarship)
2. Submit your official transcript and SAT/ACT scores
3. Write a 500-word essay: "How does financial literacy help you achieve your goals?"
4. Provide a letter of recommendation from a teacher or counselor

Winners will be announced on March 30, 2025. Scholarships are disbursed directly to your institution for tuition and fees.

Learn more: [Scholarship FAQs](https://westminstercredit.com/scholarship-faq) | [Application Guidelines](https://westminstercredit.com/scholarship-guidelines)

This is Westminster''s way of investing in the next generation. We believe education opens doors, and we''re proud to support students in our region.

Have questions? Email scholarships@westminstercredit.com or call (555) 234-0098.

Best regards,
Westminster Credit Union Communications Team
Westminster Credit Union
1500 Oak Street
Portland, OR 97214

You''re receiving this email as a member of Westminster Credit Union or as a family member of a member. [Unsubscribe](https://westminstercredit.com/email-preferences) | [Privacy Policy](https://westminstercredit.com/privacy)', NULL, 'null', null, null, null, null, ARRAY['["$2','500 to $10','000 per recipient','Application Deadline: January 15',' 2025','You''re receiving this email as a member of Westminster Credit Union"]']::TEXT[], ARRAY['["Scholarship program is a genuine community initiative with real dollar amounts and clear eligibility criteria — legitimate charitable marketing','Detailed application requirements (essay',' transcripts',' recommendations) are typical of real scholarships — demonstrates substance',' not a quick credential grab','Sender domain matches credit union',' member audience is clearly identified',' unsubscribe and privacy links provided"]']::TEXT[], 'This is a legitimate scholarship program announcement from Westminster Credit Union. The email describes a real educational grant program with specific award amounts ($2,500–$10,000), number of scholarships (30), eligibility requirements (3.0+ GPA, member or family), and a clear application deadline (January 15, 2025). The application process requires substantive materials (transcripts, essay, recommendation letter), which is standard for legitimate scholarships. The sender address matches the credit union''s domain, the audience is clearly identified (members and their families), and unsubscribe and privacy options are provided. The call to action is to apply, not to verify credentials or provide sensitive account information. This is genuine community outreach marketing.', 'generated', 'v1')
ON CONFLICT (card_id) DO NOTHING;

